trans-unit.source: Provides common functionality across communication protocols for creating <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> objects from classes that are identified as Web services.
trans-unit.target: Fornece a funcionalidade comum entre os protocolos de comunicação para a criação de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> objetos das classes que são identificados como serviços da Web.

trans-unit.source: The abstract ProtocolReflector class and its concrete derived classes create <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects from classes that are identified as Web services with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: A classe abstrata de ProtocolReflector e seu concreto criar classes derivadas <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>objetos das classes que são identificados como serviços Web com o <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute>atributo.</xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: Each concrete ProtocolReflector-derived class generates <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects according to a specified communication protocol; ProtocolReflector provides common functionality regardless of the protocol.
trans-unit.target: Cada classe concreta derivado ProtocolReflector gera objetos <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>acordo com um protocolo de comunicação especificado. ProtocolReflector fornece a funcionalidade comum independentemente do protocolo.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: An output <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can be used to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> method or one of the available overloads.
trans-unit.target: Uma saída <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>instância pode ser usada para gerar um documento WSDL Web Services Description Language () com o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A>método ou uma das sobrecargas disponíveis.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can also be used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class and related classes to generate client proxy code or abstract server code.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>instância também pode ser usada pelo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>e classes relacionadas ao gerar o proxy do cliente de código ou abstrair o código do servidor.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The ProtocolReflector class uses the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> to create a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> for each binding it identifies in the Web service class.
trans-unit.target: A classe ProtocolReflector usa o <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>para criar uma <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>para cada associação identifica na classe de serviço da Web.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: If that attribute is not present, the ProtocolReflector class creates a single binding for the entire class.
trans-unit.target: Se esse atributo não estiver presente, a classe ProtocolReflector cria uma associação simples para a classe inteira.

trans-unit.source: For each Web service method (a method in the Web service class appearing with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) belonging to a binding, a class derived from ProtocolReflector generates an operation and associated messages that are added to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> object.
trans-unit.target: Método de serviço para cada Web (um método na classe de serviço da Web que aparecem com o <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) que pertencem a uma associação, uma classe derivada de ProtocolReflector gera uma operação e mensagens associadas que são adicionadas para o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>objeto.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a developer uses these classes indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector> class, instead of directly invoking classes derived from ProtocolReflector.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, um desenvolvedor usa essas classes indiretamente por meio de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector>classe, em vez de invocar diretamente classes derivadas de ProtocolReflector.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector>
